{
"#name"
:
{
"ondb"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"类型化知识图谱 · 基于 TSV 追加日志的实体与关系管理"
,
"en"
:
"Typed knowledge graph · entity & relation management via TSV append-only log"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x ondb add --type Person --name Alice [--id p_001] [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb get --id p_001 [--json]"
,
"x ondb set --id p_001 status=active"
,
"x ondb rm --id p_001"
,
"x ondb link --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001 [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb unlink --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001 [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb linked --id proj_001 [--rel has_task] [--direction incoming] [--json]"
,
"x ondb ls [--type Task] [--json]"
,
"x ondb query --type Task --where status=open [--where priority=high] [--json]"
,
"x ondb schema add \"type:Task:required:title,status\" [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb schema ls [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb validate [--dir dir]"
,
"x ondb compact [--dir dir]"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"基于 TSV 追加日志的类型化知识图谱工具。所有数据以 TSV 行追加到日志文件中，\n用 awk 完成查询、遍历和校验，无需 Python 依赖。\n\nTSV 日志格式（tab 分隔），每行一条指令：\n- add <type> <id> <epoch_ms> <key1> <val1> <key2> <val2>...  — 创建实体\n- set <id> <epoch_ms> <key> <val> [<key2> <val2>...]         — 更新属性\n- rm  <id> <epoch_ms>                                        — 删除实体\n- link <from> <rel> <to> <epoch_ms>                          — 建立关系\n- unlink <from> <rel> <to> <epoch_ms>                        — 移除关系\n- # 开头为注释，空行忽略\nID 默认使用 x uuid 生成，时间戳使用 x epoch ms 获取。\n文件管理：使用 --dir <dir> 指定数据目录，自动管理 snapshot.<ms> + log.<ms> 模式。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Typed knowledge graph tool based on TSV append-only log. All data is appended as TSV lines,\nwith awk for querying, traversing and validation — no Python dependency.\n\nTSV log format (tab-separated), one directive per line:\n- add <type> <id> <epoch_ms> <key1> <val1> <key2> <val2>...  — create entity\n- set <id> <epoch_ms> <key> <val> [<key2> <val2>...]         — update property\n- rm  <id> <epoch_ms>                                        — delete entity\n- link <from> <rel> <to> <epoch_ms>                          — create relation\n- unlink <from> <rel> <to> <epoch_ms>                        — remove relation\n- # starts comment, empty lines ignored\nIDs default to x uuid; timestamps use x epoch ms.\nFile management: use --dir <dir> for data directory with snapshot.<ms> + log.<ms> pattern.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"日志是追加式的：执行命令时追加行到 graph.tsv 文件，查询时用 awk 全量重放计算当前状态。\n适合中小规模知识图谱（数千实体以内）；大规模场景建议迁移到 SQLite。\n"
,
"en"
:
"The log is append-only: commands append lines to graph.tsv; queries replay the full log via awk to compute current state.\nSuitable for small-to-medium graphs (up to thousands of entities); for larger graphs, consider SQLite.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"与 digraph 模块互补：ondb 管理实体和关系的 CRUD；digraph 管理执行状态和依赖调度。\n可用 x digraph next --file graph.tsv 在 ondb 日志上计算可执行结点。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Complementary to digraph: ondb manages entity & relation CRUD; digraph manages execution state and dependency scheduling.\nUse x digraph next --file graph.tsv to compute executable nodes on an ondb log.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"属性值中的 tab 用 \\t 转义，换行用 \\n 转义，反斜杠用 \\\\ 转义。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Escape tab as \\t, newline as \\n, and backslash as \\\\ in property values.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"使用 --dir <dir> 指定数据目录后，数据文件为 dir/ondb.tsv，schema 文件为 dir/schema.tsv。\n目录模式支持 snapshot.<epoch_ms> + log.<epoch_ms> 增量管理，用 compact 压缩。\n"
,
"en"
:
"With --dir <dir>, data files go to dir/ondb.tsv and schema to dir/schema.tsv.\nDirectory mode supports snapshot.<epoch_ms> + log.<epoch_ms> incremental management; use compact to compress.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"使用 schema add 定义约束后，validate 会自动检查：必填属性 (required)、禁止属性 (forbidden)、\n枚举值 (enum)、关系类型约束 (from_types/to_types)、基数约束 (cardinality)、无环约束 (acyclic)。\n"
,
"en"
:
"After defining constraints via schema add, validate checks: required properties, forbidden properties,\nenum values, relation type constraints (from_types/to_types), cardinality, and acyclic constraints.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"SQLite 模式（默认关闭）：创建标记文件 $___X_CMD_ROOT_DATA/sqlite/mode/sqlite_enable 即可开启。\n开启后查询自动使用 SQLite 索引加速，compact 产出 ondb.db。不开启则保持 AWK 重放。\n"
,
"en"
:
"SQLite mode (off by default): create marker file $___X_CMD_ROOT_DATA/sqlite/mode/sqlite_enable to enable.\nQueries use SQLite indexes for acceleration; compact produces ondb.db. Without it, AWK replay is used.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --type Person --name Alice"
,
"cn"
:
"创建一个 Person 实体"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --dir mydata --type Task --name \"Fix bug\" --id task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"创建 Task 并指定 ID 和数据目录"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"关联项目与任务"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb unlink --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"移除项目与任务的关系"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb ls --type Task"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有 Task 实体"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb query --type Task --where status=open --json"
,
"cn"
:
"查询 status=open 的 Task，JSON 输出"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb linked --id proj_001 --direction incoming"
,
"cn"
:
"查看谁关联了 proj_001"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb get --id p_001 --json"
,
"cn"
:
"获取实体详情（JSON）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb set --id task_001 status=done"
,
"cn"
:
"更新实体属性"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"type:Task:required:title,status\""
,
"cn"
:
"定义 Task 必填属性"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb validate --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"校验目录中的图谱与 schema"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb compact --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"压缩日志为快照"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Entity"
:
[
"add"
,
"get"
,
"set"
,
"rm"
]
,
"#subcmd:Relation"
:
[
"link"
,
"unlink"
,
"linked"
]
,
"#subcmd:Query"
:
[
"ls"
,
"query"
,
"validate"
]
,
"#subcmd:Manage"
:
[
"compact"
,
"schema"
]
,
"add"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"创建一个新实体并追加到日志文件。位置参数（-- 之后）作为 prop=val 属性对。"
,
"en"
:
"Create a new entity and append to the log file. Positional args (after --) are prop=val pairs."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --type Person --name Alice"
,
"cn"
:
"创建 Person 实体（自动生成 UUID）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --type Project --name \"My Project\" --id proj_001"
,
"cn"
:
"创建 Project 并指定 ID"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --type Task --name \"Write docs\" priority=high due=2026-06-01"
,
"cn"
:
"创建 Task 并设置多个属性"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb add --dir mydata --type Person --name Bob --id p_002"
,
"cn"
:
"在指定数据目录创建实体"
}
]
,
"--type"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"实体类型（如 Person, Task, Project, Event, Document）"
}
}
,
"--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定实体 ID（不指定则自动生成 UUID）"
}
}
,
"--name"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"实体名称（等同于 name=xxx 属性的简写）"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径（使用 dir/ondb.tsv）"
}
}
}
,
"get"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"根据 ID 获取实体的当前状态（重放日志计算最新属性）"
,
"en"
:
"Get current entity state by ID (replays log to compute latest properties)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb get --id p_001"
,
"cn"
:
"获取 p_001 实体详情"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb get --id p_001 --json"
,
"cn"
:
"获取实体详情（JSON 格式）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb get --dir mydata --id task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"从指定目录获取实体"
}
]
,
"--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Entity ID"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format"
}
}
}
,
"set"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"更新实体属性，追加 set 行到日志。位置参数为 key=val 属性对，可同时更新多个属性。"
,
"en"
:
"Update entity properties, append a set line to the log. Positional args are key=val pairs; multiple properties can be updated at once."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb set --id task_001 status=done"
,
"cn"
:
"将 task_001 状态设为 done"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb set --id p_001 email=alice@example.com phone=1234"
,
"cn"
:
"同时更新多个属性"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb set --dir mydata --id task_001 priority=high"
,
"cn"
:
"更新指定目录中的实体属性"
}
]
,
"--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Entity ID"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"rm"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"删除实体，追加 rm 行到日志（关系不受影响，查询时自动跳过已删除实体）"
,
"en"
:
"Delete entity, append an rm line to the log (relations preserved but skipped in queries)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb rm --id p_001"
,
"cn"
:
"删除 p_001 实体"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb rm --dir mydata --id task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"删除指定目录中的实体"
}
]
,
"--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Entity ID"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"link"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"在两个实体间建立有向关系，追加 link 行到日志。\n位置参数（-- 之后）作为关系属性 key=val，key 不能包含 = 号。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Create a directed relation between two entities, append a link line to the log.\nPositional args (after --) are link properties as key=val; key must not contain =.\n"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"建立项目到任务的关系"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --from p_001 --rel assigned_to --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"指派人员到任务"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --from task_001 --rel blocks --to task_002"
,
"cn"
:
"建立任务阻塞关系"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --from p_001 --rel attendee_of --to event_001 -- status=accepted"
,
"cn"
:
"建立带属性的关系（RSVP 状态）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb link --dir mydata --from p_001 --rel member_of --to team_001"
,
"cn"
:
"在指定目录建立关系"
}
]
,
"--from"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"起始实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Source entity ID"
}
}
,
"--rel"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"关系类型（如 has_task, assigned_to, blocks, member_of, depends_on）"
}
}
,
"--to"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"目标实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Target entity ID"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"unlink"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"移除两个实体间的关系，追加 unlink 行到日志"
,
"en"
:
"Remove a relation between two entities, append an unlink line to the log"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb unlink --from proj_001 --rel has_task --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"移除项目与任务的关系"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb unlink --dir mydata --from p_001 --rel assigned_to --to task_001"
,
"cn"
:
"移除指定目录中的关系"
}
]
,
"--from"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"起始实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Source entity ID"
}
}
,
"--rel"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"关系类型"
}
}
,
"--to"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"目标实体 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Target entity ID"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"linked"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查询实体的关联实体（支持方向过滤和关系类型过滤）"
,
"en"
:
"Query related entities (with direction and relation type filters)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
