"cmd"
:
"x ondb ls --type Person --json"
,
"cn"
:
"列出 Person 并以 JSON 输出"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb ls --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"列出指定目录中的实体"
}
]
,
"--type"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按类型过滤（如 Person, Task, Project）"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出（默认）"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format (default)"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format"
}
}
}
,
"query"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按类型和属性值过滤查询实体。--where 可多次使用表示 AND 条件。"
,
"en"
:
"Query entities by type and property value filters. Use --where multiple times for AND conditions."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb query --type Task --where status=open"
,
"cn"
:
"查询所有 status=open 的 Task"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb query --type Task --where status=open --where priority=high"
,
"cn"
:
"多条件 AND 查询"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb query --where status=active --json"
,
"cn"
:
"查询 status=active 的所有类型实体，JSON 输出"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb query --dir mydata --type Person --where department=eng"
,
"cn"
:
"查询指定目录中的实体"
}
]
,
"--type"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按类型过滤"
}
}
,
"--where"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"属性过滤条件（key=val），可多次使用表示 AND"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format"
}
}
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"validate"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"校验图谱完整性。基础检查包括悬空关系引用、重复 ID 等。\n当 schema.tsv 存在时，自动加载并校验：必填属性 (required)、禁止属性 (forbidden)、\n枚举值 (enum)、关系类型约束 (from_types/to_types)、基数约束 (cardinality)、无环约束 (acyclic)。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Validate graph integrity. Basic checks include dangling relation refs, duplicate IDs, etc.\nWhen schema.tsv exists, automatically loads and validates: required properties, forbidden properties,\nenum values, relation type constraints (from_types/to_types), cardinality, and acyclic constraints.\n"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb validate"
,
"cn"
:
"校验当前图谱"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb validate --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"校验指定目录（含 schema）"
}
]
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"compact"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"将当前日志压缩为快照文件（snapshot.<epoch_ms>），后续变更将写入新的 log.<epoch_ms>"
,
"en"
:
"Compact current log into a snapshot file (snapshot.<epoch_ms>); subsequent changes go to new log.<epoch_ms>"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb compact --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"压缩指定数据目录"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb compact --dir mydata"
,
"cn"
:
"compact 同时产出 ondb.db（需开启 SQLite 模式）"
}
]
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径"
}
}
}
,
"schema"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"管理类型约束和关系规则定义。约束保存在 schema.tsv 中，validate 时自动加载。\n约束指令使用冒号分隔格式：\n- type:TypeName:required:prop1,prop2       — 必填属性\n- type:TypeName:forbidden:prop1,prop2       — 禁止属性\n- type:TypeName:enum:prop:val1,val2,val3    — 枚举值约束\n- relation:RelName:from_types:Type1,Type2   — 关系来源类型\n- relation:RelName:to_types:Type1,Type2     — 关系目标类型\n- relation:RelName:cardinality:one_to_one   — 基数约束 (one_to_one|one_to_many|many_to_one|many_to_many)\n- relation:RelName:acyclic:1                — 无环约束\n"
,
"en"
:
"Manage type constraints and relation rules. Constraints are stored in schema.tsv, loaded automatically by validate.\nDirective format uses colon-separated fields:\n- type:TypeName:required:prop1,prop2       — required properties\n- type:TypeName:forbidden:prop1,prop2       — forbidden properties\n- type:TypeName:enum:prop:val1,val2,val3    — enum constraint\n- relation:RelName:from_types:Type1,Type2   — relation source types\n- relation:RelName:to_types:Type1,Type2     — relation target types\n- relation:RelName:cardinality:one_to_one   — cardinality (one_to_one|one_to_many|many_to_one|many_to_many)\n- relation:RelName:acyclic:1                — acyclic constraint\n"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"type:Task:required:title,status\""
,
"cn"
:
"添加 Task 必填属性约束"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"type:Task:enum:status:open,in_progress,done\""
,
"cn"
:
"添加 Task 状态枚举约束"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"type:Task:forbidden:secret\""
,
"cn"
:
"添加 Task 禁止属性"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"relation:blocks:from_types:Task\""
,
"cn"
:
"限制 blocks 关系的来源类型为 Task"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"relation:has_task:cardinality:one_to_many\""
,
"cn"
:
"添加 has_task 基数约束"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema add \"relation:blocks:acyclic:1\""
,
"cn"
:
"添加 blocks 关系无环约束"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema ls"
,
"cn"
:
"查看当前 schema 定义"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema --dir mydata ls"
,
"cn"
:
"查看指定目录的 schema"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x ondb schema --dir mydata define-type-col Task id title status"
,
"cn"
:
"定义 Task 的固定列"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Schema"
:
[
"add"
,
"ls"
,
"define-type-col"
]
,
"-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"数据目录路径（自动使用 dir/schema.tsv）"
}
}
}
,
